{
  "info": {
    "name": "Employee Management API",
    "description": "Colección para probar todos los endpoints de la Employee Management API.\n\n**Flujo recomendado:**\n1. Ejecutar «Login (Admin)» — el token se guarda automáticamente.\n2. Usar cualquier endpoint de Employees sin configuración adicional.\n3. Para probar restricciones de rol, ejecutar «Register» y luego «Login (User)».",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "employeeId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (User)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"User1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registra un nuevo usuario con rol User. Devuelve un JWT listo para usar."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('Token guardado en variable de colección.');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login con el admin sembrado por defecto. El token JWT se guarda automáticamente en la variable `token` de la colección."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('Token de Admin guardado.');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (User)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"User1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login con un usuario de rol User (previamente creado con Register). Permite verificar que POST/PUT/DELETE retornan 403."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('Token de User guardado.');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Employees",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET All Employees",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/employees",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "employees"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve todos los empleados con su historial de posiciones y bono anual calculado.\n\nRoles permitidos: Admin, User."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Response is array', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Employee by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/employees/{{employeeId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "employees", "{{employeeId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve un empleado por ID. Retorna 404 si no existe.\n\nRoles permitidos: Admin, User.\n\nModifica la variable `employeeId` de la colección para apuntar al ID deseado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 or 404', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 404]);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Create Employee (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ada Lovelace\",\n  \"currentPosition\": 1,\n  \"salary\": 5000.00,\n  \"departmentId\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/employees",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "employees"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo empleado. Retorna 201 con el empleado creado.\n\n**currentPosition:** 1 = Regular (bono 10%), 2 = Manager (bono 20%), 3 = SeniorManager (bono 25%)\n\nRol requerido: Admin. Con token de User retorna 403."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('employeeId', json.id);",
                  "        console.log('employeeId actualizado a: ' + json.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status 201 or 403', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([201, 403]);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Update Employee (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ada Lovelace (actualizada)\",\n  \"currentPosition\": 2,\n  \"salary\": 7000.00,\n  \"departmentId\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/employees/{{employeeId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "employees", "{{employeeId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza un empleado existente. Retorna 200 con los datos actualizados o 404 si no existe.\n\nRol requerido: Admin. Con token de User retorna 403."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200, 404 or 403', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 404, 403]);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE Employee (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/employees/{{employeeId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "employees", "{{employeeId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Elimina un empleado por ID. Retorna 204 si se eliminó correctamente o 404 si no existe.\n\nRol requerido: Admin. Con token de User retorna 403."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 204, 404 or 403', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([204, 404, 403]);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
